5. MODULES OF THE SYSTEM

5.1 User Profile Module

This module collects user information such as:

* Budget
* Travel duration
* Preferred destinations
* Food preferences
* Transportation preferences
* Interests and hobbies

Example:

```text
Budget: ₹20,000
Duration: 3 Days
Interest: Beaches and Adventure
```

---
 5.2 Tourist Recommendation Module

This module recommends tourist destinations using ontology-based knowledge representation.

Example:

| Interest          | Recommended Places |
| ----------------- | ------------------ |
| Beaches           | Goa, Pondicherry   |
| Historical Places | Hampi, Jaipur      |
| Nature            | Ooty, Munnar       |

---

5.3 Food Recommendation Module

The system recommends local cuisines and restaurants based on destination and user food preferences.

Example:

| Destination | Food Recommendation |
| ----------- | ------------------- |
| Hyderabad   | Biryani             |
| Goa         | Seafood             |
| Italy       | Pizza and Pasta     |

---

 5.4 Route Optimization Module

This module determines efficient travel routes using AI search algorithms.

Algorithms used:

* A* Search
* Dijkstra Algorithm
* Genetic Algorithms

Objectives:

* Minimize travel time
* Minimize travel cost
* Optimize route efficiency

---

5.5 Cost Assessment Module

The system estimates total trip cost using:

* Hotel cost
* Transportation cost
* Food expenses
* Entry fees
* Miscellaneous expenses

Formula:

Total Cost = Hotel + Food + Transport + Miscellaneous

---

5.6 Personalized Tour Planning Module

This module generates customized itineraries.

Example:

| Day   | Activities            |
| ----- | --------------------- |
| Day 1 | Beach Visit + Seafood |
| Day 2 | Museum + Shopping     |
| Day 3 | Adventure Activities  |

